                        "displayName": "Wes McKinney",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "America/New_York"
                    },
                    "body": "As I've dug into this, I believe it may be better to defer writing to implementations of OutputStream, ReadableFile, so it might be better to close this. For example, {{FixedSizeBufferOutputStream}} supports a parallel memcpy to CPU memory. We can keep thinking about it until we've hardened some of the issues around the JIRAs attached to ARROW-1055",
